{"id": "ChIJlRFdeNK-woARxLpSqbnrluQ", "rating": 4.1, "userRatingCount": 73, "displayName": {"text": "BAIT", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Cool boutique showcasing sneakers, along with streetwear, T-shirts & collectible toys.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJlRFdeNK-woARxLpSqbnrluQ/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNXNU5lRXpnRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 years ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Lots of awesome high end kicks, apparel and collectibles. I’m mostly interested in the latter and they had plenty on display. Most of it was limited to Medicom bearbrick stuff but there were some stand out pieces I never saw before.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Lots of awesome high end kicks, apparel and collectibles. I’m mostly interested in the latter and they had plenty on display. Most of it was limited to Medicom bearbrick stuff but there were some stand out pieces I never saw before.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Avedon Arcade", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104515656010013725663/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxSzQA0TQBmHRINzbtr-asbWLMt6zpxy5b-XtLj5eWVvaUZPR1=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2022-02-18T20:00:00.176526Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNXNU5lRXpnRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNXNU5lRXpnRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bed2785d1195:0xe496ebb9a952bac4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJlRFdeNK-woARxLpSqbnrluQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25SRE5tWjJRbkk1TmtvMVQxQnBUbTlKY0c1cE0xRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "10 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "First time online purchaser from this retail shop and it is a trusted business. They have a great catalog of merchandise and their customer service is attentive, fast and helpful. I highly recommend this business!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "First time online purchaser from this retail shop and it is a trusted business. They have a great catalog of merchandise and their customer service is attentive, fast and helpful. I highly recommend this business!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Spencer Linick", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100124671451977871056/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI3JhF2Z5c40mfbJN6MOEoGv_xeYB3UHGacyGERtdNosOoyXw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-09-03T17:21:00.325777998Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25SRE5tWjJRbkk1TmtvMVQxQnBUbTlKY0c1cE0xRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25SRE5tWjJRbkk1TmtvMVQxQnBUbTlKY0c1cE0xRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bed2785d1195:0xe496ebb9a952bac4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJlRFdeNK-woARxLpSqbnrluQ/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNlcmQyZHRRRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 years ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Love this store, the selection is beautiful. Unfortunately the customer service is not what I expected which sucks because I truly love the company. I think they should carefully select who works at their store because it could jeopardize sales and conversion. My husband and I were so excited but the worker was rude and I had to write a review because she left us with a bad energy- thinking about our experience  even hours after leaving. The worker had  blonde hair and short of Latina descent - I would describe her as grumpy, rude and not amicable at all. I truly wish to come back but I’ll shop online for now because my energy is everything to me. Please relay this to the worker I truly feel she has to be talked to.\n\nPros! Great selection of shoes/ company\nCons! Young environment which could be great but immature behavior in this area\n\nIn addition came to the store it had a sign that it would be closed til 130 came back and the store was completely closed and before hand when I first came the employees inside had no respect to even come to the door and at least say why?", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Love this store, the selection is beautiful. Unfortunately the customer service is not what I expected which sucks because I truly love the company. I think they should carefully select who works at their store because it could jeopardize sales and conversion. My husband and I were so excited but the worker was rude and I had to write a review because she left us with a bad energy- thinking about our experience  even hours after leaving. The worker had  blonde hair and short of Latina descent - I would describe her as grumpy, rude and not amicable at all. I truly wish to come back but I’ll shop online for now because my energy is everything to me. Please relay this to the worker I truly feel she has to be talked to.\n\nPros! Great selection of shoes/ company\nCons! Young environment which could be great but immature behavior in this area\n\nIn addition came to the store it had a sign that it would be closed til 130 came back and the store was completely closed and before hand when I first came the employees inside had no respect to even come to the door and at least say why?", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Bossy Chic", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109833478970158689633/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAxpAW-iNa4CI0HTBa_IHeLKVOzcaNNpuYxDeJ_7t6q_Jp4PQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2022-11-19T21:50:14.990728Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNlcmQyZHRRRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNlcmQyZHRRRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bed2785d1195:0xe496ebb9a952bac4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJlRFdeNK-woARxLpSqbnrluQ/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUMtMWZ2RWtnRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 years ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Online order arrived horribly, ridiculously damaged. The box was fine so the damage was not due to the shipping company, there was just no packaging inside.\n\nSent them pictures, requested a return, and they basically said they don't care and refuse to replace the items.\n\nI highly recommend ordering whatever you are looking for from someone else if you want it to arrive intact.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Online order arrived horribly, ridiculously damaged. The box was fine so the damage was not due to the shipping company, there was just no packaging inside.\n\nSent them pictures, requested a return, and they basically said they don't care and refuse to replace the items.\n\nI highly recommend ordering whatever you are looking for from someone else if you want it to arrive intact.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Brian Byrom", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108405157256503824654/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDjjcfQ2pIUAgoQAAuorbs97MEdETkkel_RXLeu4NBn_N03uqr=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2022-11-09T16:16:41.425027Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUMtMWZ2RWtnRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUMtMWZ2RWtnRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bed2785d1195:0xe496ebb9a952bac4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJlRFdeNK-woARxLpSqbnrluQ/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURBcW9mS1pBEAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 years ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "I love coming into Drip to check out the selection.  Their ladies' shoes/apparel section has really grown and I've made a couple of purchases now that I'm very happy with.  Staff is always friendly and very helpful in helping me try on the size that I need.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I love coming into Drip to check out the selection.  Their ladies' shoes/apparel section has really grown and I've made a couple of purchases now that I'm very happy with.  Staff is always friendly and very helpful in helping me try on the size that I need.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Carmelo Behan", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100542246008324078375/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMu040RF_aiTWb8RbkZZRw-M6ltZ2cjtjMcDMYq3yYSGvVv6c=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2018-04-09T23:20:36.996Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURBcW9mS1pBEAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURBcW9mS1pBEAE!2m1!1s0x80c2bed2785d1195:0xe496ebb9a952bac4"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJlRFdeNK-woARxLpSqbnrluQ/photos/AWCwyditCcYYNrwIkZcp6T-6ulWhsQboPdO-fO2ayKo_Nz9htJWHeD52nDv6Kv3tYjM-7chcZ_DOHvm_fLBfkjjwpp00qUXPPJmsPIMhIu8Tmw4D-w4n0gmgul9b35YWVYjuD3bHJtlseOyMbHBo6Dr5YUFkwVRmEtBzjmK1CB8-wsm2LkQ-hynvvEoRXix29njknfh4PQKQTt1KSI5UFVF7-OMQqkoShiPW5vigC1wW28IfDEy_qWjHV-Ip8NCTXlnCe2iCuL-eWAvnRGckXqUUqZjFoYo-9ZppFpbGw09-vqcLpIMa_2YraIwXqs-LHqpORDmYPgaKn7Hct6lNlRXrTr6eSvwh7bL_X0LALSB2K2-7n4GMdgqJnG7El0a2k9IfzEw-SPyVrRNsLSz0iVBUjPgF7HfstN4KuKwpeLroLYvE6z5a", "widthPx": 4032, "heightPx": 3024, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Nicolas Dalmar", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/115201466361972880965", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVpILwO3jnOsGH9gBh6LSQF6Xkb0WgVVqd6gG8ilWNWHe1tFExA=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgID4tOzAowE&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/pl